<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:59:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市坚挺，欧元受法国大选僵局困扰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</link><description>亚洲股市周一小幅走高，因投资者对美国 9 月降息信心增强，而法国大选表明议会将出现悬浮议会，欧元则面临政治不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总理欧尔班抵达北京与中国国家主席习近平举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</link><description>匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克托新闻负责人告诉国家通讯社 MTI，匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多周一抵达北京，与中国国家主席习近平举行会谈。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金与正称韩国演习是挑衅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</link><description>据朝中社周一报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹金与正表示，韩国最近在两国边境附近进行的军事演习是不可原谅的明显挑衅。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乐观情绪高涨，软着陆步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年温布尔登网球公开赛：第 8 天比赛顺序，德约科维奇和雷巴基纳在比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-rybakina-face-tricky-opponents-reach-wimbledon-last-eight-2024-07-07/</link><description>温网第四轮比赛将于周一在全英俱乐部结束。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 18:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-rybakina-face-tricky-opponents-reach-wimbledon-last-eight-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年温网：第 7 天阿尔卡拉斯、辛纳和拉杜卡努的比赛顺序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/confident-alcaraz-faces-aggressive-humbert-wimbledons-fourth-round-2024-07-06/</link><description>温网比赛周日在全英俱乐部继续进行，世界顶尖选手将在伦敦争夺大满贯四分之一决赛的席位。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 20:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/confident-alcaraz-faces-aggressive-humbert-wimbledons-fourth-round-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>王在温网第三轮击败泪流满面的达特</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wang-defeats-tearful-dart-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-06/</link><description>周六，本土热门选手哈里特·达特在温布尔登网球公开赛上未能突破中国选手王新宇的防守，最终以 2-6 7-5 6-3 输掉了第三轮比赛，她在网前擦干了眼泪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 16:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wang-defeats-tearful-dart-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪收购泰国经销商Rever Automotive 20%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-acquires-20-stake-thai-dealer-rever-automotive-2024-07-06/</link><description>周六，中国比亚迪公司表示，将收购泰国当地经销商 Rever Automotive 20% 的股份，泰国是比亚迪在中国以外最大的市场，比亚迪是电动汽车市场的领导者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-acquires-20-stake-thai-dealer-rever-automotive-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>达赖喇嘛89岁了，流亡藏人担心没有他的未来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/dalai-lama-turns-89-exiled-tibetans-fear-future-without-him-2024-07-06/</link><description>在印度北部雪山下的一座寺院里，受托保护达赖喇嘛并预言其人民未来的佛教僧人忧心忡忡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 11:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/dalai-lama-turns-89-exiled-tibetans-fear-future-without-him-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车集团对欧盟反补贴关税“强烈不满”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-autos-group-strongly-dissatisfied-with-eu-anti-subsidy-tariffs-2024-07-06/</link><description>中国汽车工业协会（CAAM）在周六的一份声明中表示，该协会对欧盟提出的反补贴关税“强烈不满”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 11:34:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-autos-group-strongly-dissatisfied-with-eu-anti-subsidy-tariffs-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>轩尼诗所有者路威酩轩集团表示，对中国干邑白兰地的调查是对欧盟汽车关税的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-cognac-probe-is-reaction-eu-car-tariffs-says-hennessy-owner-lvmh-2024-07-06/</link><description>轩尼诗干邑白兰地所有者路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 财务主管周六表示，中国对欧洲干邑白兰地行业的反倾销调查是针对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的针锋相对的反应。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 10:42:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-cognac-probe-is-reaction-eu-car-tariffs-says-hennessy-owner-lvmh-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>ASML前首席执行官表示中美芯片大战将继续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-asml-ceo-says-us-china-chip-fight-will-continue-2024-07-06/</link><description>最近退休的半导体设备制造商ASML首席执行官周六在接受荷兰BNR广播电台采访时表示，美中在计算机芯片方面的争端是意识形态的，而不是基于事实的，而且它们将继续下去。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 10:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-asml-ceo-says-us-china-chip-fight-will-continue-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>达赖喇嘛89岁生日否认健康谣言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dalai-lama-dismisses-health-rumours-89th-birthday-2024-07-06/</link><description>达赖喇嘛周六表示，他正在从膝盖手术中恢复，感觉“身体健康”，在他89岁生日之际否认了有关健康状况不佳的谣言。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 08:35:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/dalai-lama-dismisses-health-rumours-89th-birthday-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾海岸警卫队称中国在南海抛锚“巨轮”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-anchors-monster-ship-in-south-china-sea-philippine-coast-guard-says-2024-07-06/</link><description>菲律宾海岸警卫队（PCG）周六表示，中国最大的海岸警卫队船只已停泊在南中国海的马尼拉专属经济区（EEZ），旨在恐吓其较小的亚洲邻国。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 07:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-anchors-monster-ship-in-south-china-sea-philippine-coast-guard-says-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国第二大淡水湖决口封堵工作开始</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/residents-relocated-after-dam-breach-chinas-second-largest-freshwater-lake-2024-07-06/</link><description>中国官方媒体称，周六下午，在决堤两侧水位稳定后，救援人员开始封闭中国南部第二大淡水湖的决口堤坝。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 05:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/residents-relocated-after-dam-breach-chinas-second-largest-freshwater-lake-2024-07-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>